                <h1>Nike execs texted about paying Zion Williamson more than $35,000, Avenatti alleges</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/570e8209-f3cc-46d6-8185-98f123fe7649.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="Zion&#x20;Williamson&#x20;walks&#x20;on&#x20;the&#x20;court&#x20;at&#x20;a&#x20;game&#x20;against&#x20;North&#x20;Carolina&#x20;in&#x20;March&#x20;2019.&#x20;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            Zion Williamson walks on the court at a game against North Carolina in March 2019. 

